%define theme_name Krakin

Summary:        Krakin cursor theme
Name:           krakin-cursor-theme
Version:        20100221
Release:        3.1
License:        freeware
Group:          User Interface/Desktops
URL:            https://grynays.deviantart.com/art/krakin-154925900?q=1&qo=1
